      </p></li></ul></div></div><div class="navfooter"><hr><table width="100%" summary="Navigation footer"><tr><td width="40%" align="left"><a accesskey="p" href="basic_activate.php">Prev</a> </td><td width="20%" align="center"><a accesskey="u" href="basic.php">Up</a></td><td width="40%" align="right"> <a accesskey="n" href="basic_update.php">Next</a></td></tr><tr><td width="40%" align="left" valign="top">Software Task - Activate Keyman Desktop </td><td width="20%" align="center"><a accesskey="h" href="index.php">Home</a></td><td width="40%" align="right" valign="top"> Software Task - Update Keyman Desktop</td></tr></table></div>
